<v-dialog
  v-model="visi"
  width="400" persistent
>
  <v-card>
    <v-card-text v-if="type == 'ad'">
      确定{{status ? '上架' : '下架'}}该广告吗?
    </v-card-text>
    <v-card-text v-if="type == 'coupon'">
      确定{{status ? '上架' : '下架'}}该优惠券吗？
    </v-card-text>

    <v-card-actions>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-btn
        color="primary"
        @click="offCtrl" small
      >
        确定
      </v-btn>
      <v-btn
        @click="close" small
      >
        取消
      </v-btn>
    </v-card-actions>
  </v-card>
</v-dialog>
